### Theme Variations

| Element | **Game** | **Business** |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Color | Bright, rarity colors | Navy & greys |
| FX | Parallax, coins, Lottie | Minimal |
| Icons | Cartoon | Line/system |
| Font | Rounded display | System sans |

